  "feesApplyText": "A spacious two double bedroom 1st floor modern flat in an extremely desirable location just off Windmill Hill. Within a short walking distance is Enfield Chase rail station (Great Northern line) providing direct access into Kings Cross & Moorgate in under 30mins. There is a bus stop opposite the property providing further transport links. Moments away to Enfield Town's vibrant high street providing an extensive selection of individual health and beauty shops, supermarkets, boutiques, pubs, bars and restaurants.\n\nThe property includes an Italian fitted kitchen with full integrated appliances, fridge/freezer, dishwasher, oven/hob, microwave and extractor hood. Double glazing and gas central heating.\n\nA luxury en-suite and family bathroom are fitted with porcelain tiles and under floor heating. \n\nThe development offers a private secure gated underground car park for residential use only. \n\nCouncil Tax Band E = \u00a32,586\n\n\nAdams and Styles are committed to full compliance in the letting and residential property industry. We are members of the following schemes:\n\nClient Money Protection (Safe Agent) - Licence no. A1406\nProperty Redress Scheme (PRS) - PRS012628\nAccredited Safe Agent - Licence No. A1406",
